              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Uncertainty is Given in Data Table.",
                "The Total Error in the Cross Section Values Given is",
                "The Square Root of the Sums of the Squares of the",
                "Contributing Errors.The Errors in Determination of the",
                "Count Rate at End of Bombardment were Between 2% and",
                " 9%, Depending on the Individual Case, in Target Weight",
                " +-2%, Chemical Yield +-5%,+-10% in Detector Efficiency",
                "Calibration and +-7% in Exact Time of Separation of the",
                "Niobium from Its Parent. The Error in During of",
                "Bombardment was Negligible and the Beam Spread was",
                " +-2 MeV at the Energies Used. The Error Introduced by",
                "Neglecting the Time Required For the Decay of the",
                "Metastable Isomer to the Ground State was Negligible",
                "In the Case of Nb-97 and Less Than 12% For Nb-95."
              ]
